4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in JavaScript and Python over 18 weeks. The program focuses on web development, algorithm scripting, building applications using front-end libraries, and working with APIs. Classes consist of 3 sessions per week with a favorable teacher-student ratio of 1:7. No prior coding experience is necessary, and instruction is available in both English and Spanish. Participants will gain hands-on experience by developing and presenting their own projects, culminating in a Full-Stack Developer certificate. 

